Running via docker using the instructions from here: (https://hub.docker.com/r/openlink/virtuoso-opensource-7/).
And following along with delete examples from here: (http://vos.openlinksw.com/owiki/wiki/VOS/VirtTipsAndTricksSPARQL11Delete).
The delete command, running through the conductor SPARQL query tab:
prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns>
